<view class="ga-page voice">
  <view class="ga-hero voice-hero">
    <text class="ga-hero__eyebrow">设备语音</text>
    <view class="ga-hero__title">浇水时它对你说什么</view>
    <view class="ga-hero__desc">在下方选一句拟人化文案，或自己写一句（最多 {{maxLen}} 字）。固件下次开机或拉取配置时自动生效。</view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{devices.length === 0}}" class="ga-card voice-empty">
    <text>暂无可设置的设备，请先在「设置 → 传感器绑定码」完成配网。</text>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="ga-section-title">选择设备</view>
    <view class="ga-card voice-card">
      <picker mode="selector" range="{{deviceLabels}}" value="{{deviceIndex}}" bindchange="onDeviceChange">
        <view class="voice-picker">{{deviceLabels[deviceIndex]}}</view>
      </picker>
      <view class="voice-current">
        <text class="voice-current__label">当前文案</text>
        <text class="voice-current__text" wx:if="{{!isDefault}}">{{currentMessage}}</text>
        <text class="voice-current__text voice-current__text--default" wx:else>（默认）{{defaultMessage}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="ga-section-title">预设文案</view>
    <block wx:for="{{categories}}" wx:for-item="cat" wx:key="key">
      <view class="ga-card voice-cat">
        <view class="voice-cat__head">
          <text class="voice-cat__name">{{cat.name}}</text>
          <text class="voice-cat__desc">{{cat.desc}}</text>
        </view>
        <block wx:for="{{cat.phrases}}" wx:for-item="phrase" wx:key="*this">
          <view
            class="voice-phrase {{draft === phrase ? 'voice-phrase--active' : ''}}"
            data-phrase="{{phrase}}"
            bindtap="onPickPhrase"
          >
            <text>{{phrase}}</text>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </block>

    <view class="ga-section-title">自定义</view>
    <view class="ga-card voice-card">
      <view class="voice-custom-toggle" bindtap="onToggleCustom">
        {{ customExpanded ? '收起' : '我要自己写一句' }}
      </view>
      <block wx:if="{{customExpanded}}">
        <textarea
          class="voice-textarea"
          maxlength="{{maxLen}}"
          placeholder="例如：嘿嘿，是水！我准备开始疯长啦～"
          value="{{draft}}"
          bindinput="onDraftInput"
        />
        <text class="voice-count">{{draft.length}} / {{maxLen}}</text>
      </block>
    </view>

    <view class="voice-actions">
      <view class="voice-btn voice-btn--primary {{saving ? 'voice-btn--disabled' : ''}}" bindtap="onSave">
        {{ saving ? '保存中…' : '保存到设备' }}
      </view>
      <view class="voice-btn voice-btn--ghost" bindtap="onResetDefault">恢复默认</view>
    </view>

    <view class="voice-hint">
      固件在浇水事件触发时会朗读这句话。修改后设备会在下次启动 / 周期拉取（约每 5 分钟）时同步。
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
